OL,3,CTrain drivers' union calls on
OL,4,Cgovernment to 'think again' on peak
OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,FA train drivers' union has called on
OL,8,Fthe Scottish Government to "think
OL,9,Fagain" over its decision to restore
OL,10,Fpeak time fares on Scotland's railways.
OL,12,FThe Aslef union described the
OL,13,Fgovernment's decision to end a nearly
OL,14,Fyear-long trial scrapping peak time
OL,15,Ffares as "a tax on workers".
OL,17,FThe change has seen the price of an
OL,18,Fanytime return ticket between Glasgow
OL,19,Fand Edinburgh rise from #16.20 to
OL,20,F#31.40.
