OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,FThe union added that it was a "short-
OL,8,Fsighted" decision that would damage
OL,9,Flocal economies and make it harder to
OL,10,Fmeet climate targets, and called on
OL,11,Fthe government to reverse it in the
OL,12,Fnext budget.
OL,14,FAslef Scottish organiser Kevin Lindsay
OL,15,Fsaid: "The flawed decision by First
OL,16,FMinister John Swinney and transport
OL,17,Fminister Fiona Hyslop to restore peak
OL,18,Ffares will fleece passengers and is a
OL,19,Fhuge mistake that must be rectified in
OL,20,Fthe next Scottish budget.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@HO]wD@GOU
