OL,3,CTrain drivers' union calls on
OL,4,Cgovernment to 'think again' on peak
OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,F"Peak fares are no more than a tax on
OL,8,Fworkers and removing them was a step
OL,9,Fin the right direction to make rail
OL,10,Ffares more affordable. It put more
OL,11,Fmoney in the pockets of rail
OL,12,Fpassengers.
OL,14,F"In Fiona Hyslop's own constituency,
OL,15,Fthe impact will be severe.
OL,17,F"If a worker now has to get an on-peak
OL,18,Freturn fare from Linlithgow to Glasgow
OL,19,Ffive days a week for four weeks in a
OL,20,Fmonth, they will be #166 per month
OL,21,Fworse off.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
