OL,3,CTrain drivers' union calls on
OL,4,Cgovernment to 'think again' on peak
OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,F"That is a shocking indictment of the
OL,8,Fdecision she has made and the level of
OL,9,Fthese rises in fares will impact local
OL,10,Feconomies all across Scotland as
OL,11,Fpeople see their disposable income
OL,12,Freduced."
OL,14,FMr Lindsay added that the decision
OL,15,Fwould only force more people off the
OL,16,Frailways and "back into their cars".
OL,18,F"Rail travel must be made accessible,
OL,19,Fattractive and affordable if Scotland
OL,20,Fis to shift people from road to rail
OL,21,Ftravel and meet its climate targets.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@IO]xD@NOUxD@cO]zD@AOU
