OL,3,CTrain drivers' union calls on
OL,4,Cgovernment to 'think again' on peak
OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,F"But this short-sighted decision flies
OL,8,Fin the face of our ambition to develop
OL,9,Fworld-class rail services and will
OL,10,Fundermine rail travel by pushing
OL,11,Fpeople back into their cars.
OL,13,F"The Scottish Government did not give
OL,14,Fpeople enough time to make the shift
OL,15,Ffrom road to rail. Removing peak fares
OL,16,Fwas shown to work and will work even
OL,17,Fbetter if given the time to do so.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
