OL,3,CTrain drivers' union calls on
OL,4,Cgovernment to 'think again' on peak
OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,F"The Scottish Government must think
OL,8,Fagain. In the next Scottish Budget,
OL,9,Fthey have a chance to change their
OL,10,Fmind, rectify this disastrous decision
OL,11,Fand remove peak fares on behalf of
OL,12,Fpassengers, the wider economy and the
OL,13,Fenvironment."
OL,15,FScottish Greens transport spokesperson
OL,16,FMark Ruskell said: "A lot of commuters
OL,17,Fwill have an unpleasant surprise when
OL,18,Fthey pay for their tickets this
OL,19,Fmorning and see that prices are higher
OL,20,Fthan ever.
