OL,3,CTrain drivers' union calls on
OL,4,Cgovernment to 'think again' on peak
OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,F"Peak rail fares are fundamentally
OL,8,Funfair. They disproportionately impact
OL,9,Fpeople who have no say over when they
OL,10,Fneed to travel for work or study.
OL,12,F"Bringing them back will do nothing to
OL,13,Fhelp workers or students or to
OL,14,Fencourage people out of their cars.
OL,16,F"Many regular commuters have saved
OL,17,Fhundreds of pounds on their fares over
OL,18,Fthe last year, and some of the rises
OL,19,Fthey will now face are staggering."
