OL,7,FScottish Liberal Democrat transport
OL,8,Fspokesman Daniel O'Malley said: "For
OL,9,Fmore than two years, SNP ministers
OL,10,Fhave been responsible for the
OL,11,Frailways. In that time, they have
OL,12,Fproduced a service that is as erratic
OL,13,Fas it is expensive.
OL,15,F"This SNP Government are completely
OL,16,Fout of touch. Even when Parliament
OL,17,Fvoted for the Government to reverse
OL,18,Ftheir decision to hike fares, the SNP
OL,19,Fsimply chose to ignore it.
OL,26,@pD@aOUwD@AOU
