OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,F"Scottish Liberal Democrats want a
OL,8,Freliable rail service which everyone
OL,9,Fcan afford to travel on. It's a win-
OL,10,Fwin that would bring down costs and
OL,11,Fhelp tackle the climate crisis."
OL,13,FA Transport Scotland spokeswoman said:
OL,14,F"The peak fares removal pilot was a
OL,15,Fwelcome incentive over the last 12
OL,16,Fmonths, saving many passengers
OL,17,Fhundreds and in some cases thousands
OL,18,Fof pounds during the cost-of-living
OL,19,Fcrisis.
