OL,5,Crail fares
OL,7,F"The Scottish Government would be open
OL,8,Fto consider future subsidy to remove
OL,9,Fpeak fares should UK budget
OL,10,Fallocations improve in future years.
OL,12,F"Ministers understand this will be
OL,13,Fdisappointing for many rail users,
OL,14,Fparticularly for those who cannot
OL,15,Fchoose when they travel to and from
OL,16,Fwork.
OL,18,F"That is why a 12-month discount on
OL,19,Fall ScotRail season tickets has been
OL,20,Fintroduced, available weekly, monthly
OL,21,Fand annually."
